snippet.title: Bijuria | Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari | Varun, Janhvi,Sanya, Rohit | Sonu, Tanishk, Ravi, Asees
snippet.description:
Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe giraye re bijuria, bijuria ⚡

A firecracker of a song 🧨, presenting ‘Bijuria’ from ‘Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari’! Featuring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Rohit Saraf and Sanya Malhotra in the video, the song is composed by Tanishk Bagchi and Ravi Pawar. Sung by Sonu Nigam and Asees Kaur and penned by Sonu Nigam and Tanishk Bagchi, hit play, turn it up, and let the beat take over! 🔥🎧

#Bijuria #SunnySanskariKiTulsiKumari #VarunDhawan #JanhviKapoor #SonuNigam #TanishkBagchi 

Original music composer: Ravi Pawar 
New version reimagined by : Tanishk Bagchi
Singer: Sonu Nigam
Singer: Asees Kaur
Music Producer: Tanishk Bagchi
Original Lyrics by: Sonu Nigam & Ajay Jhingran
New Version Additional Lyrics by: Tanishk Bagchi
Tabla & Dholak: Raju Sardar, Sanjiv Sen, Sharafat, Arou
Female Chorus: Shudhi Ramani, Abhiruchi Singh, Megha Bhardwaj, Nikitha Venkatesh
Male Chorus: Vivek Naik, Rahul Chitnis, Sagar Lele, Santosh Bote
Chorus Recorded at: Input One
Recording Engineer: Sameer Dharap (Input One)
Chorus Recorded at: Studio 504
Recording Engineer: Rahul M Sharma (Studio 504)
Mix and Master Engineer: Eric Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Special Thanks : Hero
Special Thanks: Sumeet Kr Tyagi
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor: Vasundhara Misra
Music Team: Heer Kamdar

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Director Of Choreography: Piyush - Shazia
Song Editor: Rishabh Shetty 
Asst Editor: Hrushi

Releasing on 2nd October, 2025

Lyrics:

Bann jaye-gi, yeh bann jaye-gi, re teri dhulania (x2)

Tujhe lage na najariya,
Kyun na odhe tu chunariya
Oh tujhe lage na najariya, odh le chunariya

Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe
Giraye re bijuria, bijuria

Bijuriaaaaa

Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe
Giraye re bijuria, bijuria

(Music)
Haye tera sharmana, tauba tera itraana
Jo bhi dekhe ho jaye woh deewana tera

Sone jaisa tan tera, uff bhola pan tera
Mujko bhi kar gaya deewana tera

O sun baki re gujariya,
Yahi bole hai dagaria
Sun baki re gujariya, bole ye dagaria

Lachke kamariya toh chhalke
Gagariya ki luti re bajaria (x2)

(Music)

Ooo…lachke kamariya toh thirke bijuria
Bachke dagariya toh girke bijuria

Oore bijuria x 2

Naino se maare chori aisan bijuria…aaahhh

Oh mujhe lage na najariya,
Maine odhe li chunariya
mujhe lage na najariya,
odhe li chunariya,
Mera hi deewana mere
dil pe fida hai…
Banungi mein dhulaniya

Dhulaniaaaaa

Mera hi deewana mere
dil pe fida hai…
Banungi mein dhulaniya

Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe
giraye re bijuria, bijuria (x2)

(Music)

Lachke kamariya toh
Bachke dagariya toh

Ohh ohh re bijuria
Naino se maare chori aisan bijuria…

Aaahhh…aaah…aaaaa!!

JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3 is coming exclusively to Crunchyroll January 2026! Watch JUJUTSU KAISEN Crunchyroll! https://got.cr/cc-jjkpv

Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Satoru Gojo, Itadori is admitted to Tokyo Jujutsu High School, an organization that fights the curses... and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a curse to exorcise a curse, a life from which he could never turn back.

Expanding upon the world created by Danny Boyle and Alex Garland in 28 Years Later but turning that world on its head - Nia DaCosta directs 28 Years Later: The Bone Temple. In a continuation of the epic story, Dr. Kelson (Ralph Fiennes) finds himself in a shocking new relationship - with consequences that could change the world as they know it - and Spike's (Alfie Williams) encounter with Jimmy Crystal (Jack O'Connell) becomes a nightmare he can't escape. In the world of The Bone Temple, the infected are no longer the greatest threat to survival - the inhumanity of the survivors can be stranger and more terrifying.

snippet.title: Nishaanchi - Official Trailer | In Cinemas - September 19 | Amazon MGM Studios India
snippet.description:
Ab tak toh bas jhalak dekhe the, ab time hai phull bawaal trailer dekhne ka! 🔥💥🥵
#Nishaanchi, Trailer Out Now.

Releasing in theatres near you on September 19🎯

Make sure you enter the world of Nishaanchi in cinemas!
Hit ‘I’m Interested’ by clicking below for exclusive offers, updates, & more on BookMyShow.

Link: 
https://bookmy.show/Nishaanchi 

Amazon MGM Studios India has announced its theatrical movie Nishaanchi, which is set to premiere on September 19. Directed by Anurag Kashyap, this raw and gritty theatrical crime drama is produced by Ajay Rai and Ranjan Singh under the banner of Jar Pictures in association with Flip Films. Nishaanchi marks the powerful acting debut of Aaishvary Thackeray who stars alongside Vedika Pinto, Monika Panwar, Mohammed Zeeshan Ayyub and Kumud Mishra in pivotal roles. Crafted for the big screen, Nishaanchi delivers a gripping, cinematic experience that delves into the complex lives of two brothers who walk starkly different paths, uncovering how their choices shape their destinies.

snippet.title: Baaghi 4 Remake - Tiger Shroff Trailer | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Baaghi 4 Remake - Tiger Shroff Trailer Reaction By Deeksha Sharma. Baaghi 4 Trailer presented Tiger Shroff like never before in Hard Hitting Action Scenes with Unexpected Sanjay Dutt Villain Character & Harnaaz Sandhu as Mysterious lover but Sonam Bajwa is still a mystery. But here comes the Big Question- 555 Tamil Film Ainthu Ainthu Ainthu can be the inspiration for Baaghi 4 Remake in Hindi. snippet.title: एकादशी स्पेशल - वक्त खराब है तो अवश्य सुनें | KHATU SHYAM BHAJAN | EKADASHI BHAJAN 2025 | Gyaras
snippet.description:
एकादशी स्पेशल - वक्त खराब है तो अवश्य सुनें | KHATU SHYAM BHAJAN | EKADASHI BHAJAN 2025 | Gyaras

Songs: Khatuwala Jab Bhi Deta Deta Chappar Faad Ke + Wo Naseebo Se Jyada De Raha Hai + Jaise Jaise Dar Pe Tere Jhukta Chala Gaya + Tere Jaisa Aur Koi Daata Nahi + Shyam Ke Darbar Se Khali Nahi Jayenge + Teri Chaukhat Pe Aana Mera Kaam Hai  


⭐⭐⭐अपने दिन को बेहतर बनाने व् अपने श्याम बाबा के नए नए सुन्दर सुन्दर भजन रोज सुनने के लिए हमारे साथ जुड़े रहे || स्वस्थ रहें मस्त रहें  || जय श्री श्याम || जय श्री कृष्णा ||⭐⭐⭐

⭐ आज कल जगह जगह विडियो में बताये/ दिखाई देने वाले किसी भी उपाय पर विश्वास न करे
भजन के माध्यम से ही बाबा श्याम से प्राथना करके अपना जीवन सफल बनाए

snippet.title: GREEN GIRL | Official Kannada Trailer | Sarthak Hegde Film | KRG Studios
snippet.description:
GREEN GIRL — a fearless, stylish take on interfaith love.

🎟 Book Tickets Now on BookMyShow: https://in.bookmyshow.com/movies/green-girl/ET00459562 
✨ In Cinemas September 12, 2025 ✨  
Audio: Kannada • Subtitles: English  

Directed by award-winning filmmaker Sarthak Hegde, GREEN GIRL is a romantic drama that explores interfaith love against the backdrop of religious strife, suppressed desires, and the lure of an illusive American Dream.
Set in coastal Karnataka, the story follows a teenage interfaith couple chasing the American Dream while caught in a storm of religious strife, hidden desires, and the pull of fundamentalism. With sweeping music, breathtaking visuals, and raw honesty, Green Girl is a fearless, emotionally charged love story.
—
Cast
Mayur Gowda • Sucharitha • Sudarshan Acharya Yekkar

snippet.title: Shinchan Meets Mahabali! 🎉 Franklin Gets a Superbike Gift | GTA 5 Malayalam Onam Special 🚀😂
snippet.description:
✨ GTA 5 Malayalam Onam Special 2025 – Franklin, Shinchan & Mahabali Storyline!
In this epic Onam episode, Shiranui surprises Franklin with a superbike gift 🚴🔥. Franklin is super happy, but Shinchan crashes the bike in his funny style 😂. Feeling sad after Franklin scolds him, Shinchan runs away in the rain 🌧️… where he meets none other than Mahabali – the King of Kerala! 👑🌴

Mahabali shows his powers, fixes Franklin’s bike, and even spawns Kinder Joy 🍫. Together they go for Onam shopping at Trevor’s fruit & vegetable shop 🥭🍌. But when the taxi villains try to attack, Mahabali uses his magic to send them flying 🚖💥. Finally, Shinchan shows a Lamborghini, and Mahabali spawns supercars for everyone 🏎️✨.

👉 Stay tuned for Part 2 – the Onam celebration with full fun, sadya, pookalam, and more! 🌸🍲

🎥 Don’t forget to LIKE 👍, SHARE, and SUBSCRIBE for more GTA 5 Malayalam funny videos with Franklin, Shinchan, and family!

snippet.title: BGMS VLOG DAY 16 | SETBACKS HIT HARD | TEAM GODLIKE
snippet.description:
Day 16 was easily our toughest and messiest so far. Nothing went our way and things spiraled out of control. The vibes were off and it really showed. Not the kind of day we wanted, but it’s part of the journey. Hoping to bounce back stronger from this mess.
#dilsegodlike #GodLike #BGMS 


Follow our Socials:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/godlike.in
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GodLike_in

snippet.title: TROPHIES ARE GONE?!
snippet.description:
Learn everything about the biggest matchmaking change in Clash of Clans history and what it means for you.
This change is coming with our next big update, but we wanted to give you a heads up so you can prepare.
For the first time ever, you will be able to choose how you want to Clash. Whether you're looking for competitive battles or a more relaxed way to play, this change gives you the freedom to pick the experience that fits your goals.

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent’s Guide:
https://supercell.com/en/parents/

snippet.title: गणपति विसर्जन स्पेशल 2025 🙏 निरोप घेतो देवा आता आज्ञा असावी Nirop Gheto Deva 🙏 Ganpati Visarjan Geet
snippet.description:
🙏 "गणपती बाप्पा मोरया... पुन्हा वर्षी लवकर या!"
हा निरोपाचा क्षण आहे भावपूर्ण, भक्तिभावाने भरलेला. गणरायाच्या विसर्जनाच्या वेळी गायले जाणारे हे खास भक्तिगीत तुमच्या मनाला स्पर्शून जाईल. 🌸

Credits:-
Singer - Sharmishtha Bhatkar
Composer - Siddhant Karawde
Lyrics - Traditional

Aarti Lyrics :-
जाहले भजन आम्ही नमितो तव चरणा।
वारुनिया विघ्ने देवा रक्षावे दीना ॥धृ॥

दास तुझे आम्ही देवा तुजलाची ध्यातो
प्रेमे करुनिया देवा गुण तुझेची गातो ॥१॥

तरी द्यावी सिद्धी देवा हेची वासना, देवा हेची वासना
रक्षुनियां सर्वां द्यावी आम्हासी आज्ञा ॥२॥

मागणे ते देवा एकची आहे आता एकची आहे
तारुनियां सकळां आम्हां कृपादृष्टी पाहे ॥३॥

जेव्हां सर्व आम्ही मिळूं ऐशा या ठाया ऐशा या ठाया
प्रेमानंदे लागू तुझी कीर्ति गावया ॥४॥

सदा ऐशी भक्ति राहो आमुच्या मनी देवा आमुच्या मनी
हेची देवा तुम्हा असे नित्य विनवणी ॥५॥

वारुनिया संकटॆ आता आमुची सारी आता आमुची सारी
कृपेची सा‌ऊली देवा दीनावरि करी ॥६॥

निरंतर आमुची चिंता तुम्हां असावी चिंता तुम्हा असावी
आम्हां सर्वांची लज्जा देवा तुम्ही रक्षावी ॥७॥

निरोप घेता आता आम्हा आज्ञा असावी देवा आज्ञा असावी
चुकले आमचे काही त्याची क्षमा असावी ॥८॥

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

mr.title: गणपति विसर्जन स्पेशल 2025 🙏 निरोप घेतो देवा आता आज्ञा असावी Nirop Gheto Deva 🙏 Ganpati Visarjan Geet
mr.description:
🙏 "गणपती बाप्पा मोरया... पुन्हा वर्षी लवकर या!"
हा निरोपाचा क्षण आहे भावपूर्ण, भक्तिभावाने भरलेला. गणरायाच्या विसर्जनाच्या वेळी गायले जाणारे हे खास भक्तिगीत तुमच्या मनाला स्पर्शून जाईल. 🌸

Credits:-
Singer - Sharmishtha Bhatkar
Composer - Siddhant Karawde
Lyrics - Traditional

Aarti Lyrics :-
जाहले भजन आम्ही नमितो तव चरणा।
वारुनिया विघ्ने देवा रक्षावे दीना ॥धृ॥

दास तुझे आम्ही देवा तुजलाची ध्यातो
प्रेमे करुनिया देवा गुण तुझेची गातो ॥१॥

तरी द्यावी सिद्धी देवा हेची वासना, देवा हेची वासना
रक्षुनियां सर्वां द्यावी आम्हासी आज्ञा ॥२॥

मागणे ते देवा एकची आहे आता एकची आहे
तारुनियां सकळां आम्हां कृपादृष्टी पाहे ॥३॥

जेव्हां सर्व आम्ही मिळूं ऐशा या ठाया ऐशा या ठाया
प्रेमानंदे लागू तुझी कीर्ति गावया ॥४॥

सदा ऐशी भक्ति राहो आमुच्या मनी देवा आमुच्या मनी
हेची देवा तुम्हा असे नित्य विनवणी ॥५॥

वारुनिया संकटॆ आता आमुची सारी आता आमुची सारी
कृपेची सा‌ऊली देवा दीनावरि करी ॥६॥

निरंतर आमुची चिंता तुम्हां असावी चिंता तुम्हा असावी
आम्हां सर्वांची लज्जा देवा तुम्ही रक्षावी ॥७॥

निरोप घेता आता आम्हा आज्ञा असावी देवा आज्ञा असावी
चुकले आमचे काही त्याची क्षमा असावी ॥८॥

snippet.title: Saiyaara (1980) Ft. Kishore Kumar full song (Old version) Old is Gold with a New Voice!
snippet.description:
Saiyaara (1980) Ft. Kishore Kumar full song (Old version) Old is Gold with a New Voice!

The full version is finally here! We converted the vocals sung amazingly by RJ Kisna into kishore da's voice using AI, and I produced the retro background music, let me know if ya'll want a breakdown of how I do these retro versions! 




🌍 Follow me here for more fun and behind the scenes:
Instagram - 
@anshuman.sharma1 |   / anshuman.sharma1  
Twitter - @anshumonsharma |   / anshumonsharma  
Facebook - @anshuman.sharma111 |   / anshuman.sharma1  

Saiyaara (1980) – Kishore Kumar's Saiyaara Full Song 
Step back in time and relive the golden era of Bollywood with Kishore Kumar's rare gem "Saiyaara" (1980). This soulful melody captures the essence of vintage romance, timeless lyrics, and the golden voice of Kishore Da that still resonates in every heart.

Whether you're a lifelong Kishore fan or discovering his magic for the first time, this song is a journey into the past that you don't want to mi

Credit goes to _Rakesh Sutradhar 🙏

[Verse 1]
Tu paas hai mere paas hai aise
Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Tu paas hai mere paas hai aise
Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Baaton mein teri main raatein bitaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

[Chorus]
Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Verse 2]
Beetey lamhon se duniya basa loon
Main toh tere aansuon ka bana hoon

Meri hansi mein teri sadaayein
Teri kahaani khud ko sunaaun

Yaadon ke taare, yaadon ke taare tootenge kaise
Mere hain jo woh roothenge kaise

Beetey dinon ki kholi kitaabein
Guzre palon ko kaise bhula dein

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Baaton mein teri main raatein bitaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

[Chorus Repeat]
Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Bridge]
Jis roz hum tum phir se milenge
Yeh saari baatein tujhse kahenge

Duniya mein chaahe ban jaayein jo bhi
Tere bina tab kuch na rahenge

[Outro]
Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Main mar hi jaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon



👇 Let us know your favorite Kishore Kumar song in the comments! 👇
💬 What memories does this song bring back for you?

snippet.title: ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता आरती | Om Jai Lakshmi Mata {With Lyrics} | #laxmi #aarti #omjailaxmimata
snippet.description:
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता आरती | Om Jai Lakshmi Mata {With Lyrics} | #laxmi #aarti #omjailaxmimata 

laxmi aarti, laxmi ki aarti, maa laxmi aarti, laxmiji aarti, laxmi ji ki aarti, laxmi aarti fast, aarti laxmi ki, laxmi maa ni aarti, laxmi aarti songs, laxmiji ni aarti, laxmi mata ki aarti, laxmi aarti lyrics, diwali laxmi aarti, aarti laxmi ji ki, laxmi mata aarti, laxmi puja aarti, laxmi aarti in hindi, vaibhav laxmi aarti, maa laxmi ji ki aarti, laxmi pujan aarti, laxmi ji ki aarti fast, om laxmi mata aarti, laxmi aarti superfast, superfast laxmi aarti, laxmi aarti with lyrics, laxmi mata ki aarti fast



















Aarti Lyrics & Meaning:
(Om Jai Lakshmi Mata, Maiya Jai Lakshmi Mata, 
Tumko Nis Din Sevat, Maiyaji Ko Nis Din Sevat, 
Har Vishnu Vidhata, Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.) 2

Glory To You, O Mother, Glory To You, Mother Lakshmi. 
Shiva, Vishnu, And Brahma Worship You Day And Night.

Uma Rama Bramhani, Tum Hi Jag Mata, 
Maiya Tum Hi Jag Mata, Surya Chandrama Dhyavat, 
Surya Chandrama Dhyavat, Narad Muni Gaata, 
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

You Are The Consort Of Vishnu, Embodied As Brahmani, 
Rudrani—The Mother Of The World
The Sun And The Moon Adore You And Saint Narada Sings For You.

Durga Roop Niranjani, Sukh Sampati Data, 
Maiya Sukh Sampati Data, Jo Koi Tumko Dhyavat, 
Jo Koi Tumko Dhyavat,  Riddhi Siddhi Dhan Pata, 
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

As Durga, You Bless People With Happiness And Wealth. 
Whoever Chants Your Name Is Bestowed With Prosperity And The Riches.

Tum Patal Nivasini, Tum Shubh Phal Data, 
Maiya Tum Shubh Phal Data, Karma Prabhav Prakashini, 
Karma Prabhav Prakashini, Jag Nidhi Hey Trata, 
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

You Are Omnipresent. You Bring Good Luck, 
Bless People With The Wealth And Pleasures.

Jis Ghar Tum Rehti Taha, Har Sadgun Aata, 
Maiya Har Sadgun Aata, Sab Sambhav Ho Jata, 
Sab Sambhav Ho Jata, Mann Nahin Ghabrata, 
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata

Wherever You Reside, Good Luck Follows. 
The Impossible Becomes Possible And The Heart Becomes Fearless.

Tum Bin Yagya Ka Paavan, Karma Na Ho Pata, 
Maiya Karma Na Ho Pata,
Khaan Paan Ka Vaibhav, Khaan Paan Ka Vaibhav, 
Sab Tumse Aata, Om Jai Lakshmi Mata

No Yagya Is Possible Without You. 
None Can Buy Garments, Food And Comfort Without You.

Shubh Gun Sundar Sukta, Kshironidhi Jata 
Maiya Kshironidhi Jata, Ratna Chaturdash Tum Bin, 
Ratna Chaturdash Tum Bin, Koi Nahin Pata, 
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

The Temple Of Good Fortune Is Beautiful. 
You Are Adorned With 14 Precious Gems That None Is Blessed With.

Maha Lakshmi Ji Ki Aarti, Jo Koi Bhi Gata, 
Maiya Jo Koi Bhi Gata, Ur Anand Samata, 
Ur Anand Samata, Paar Utar Jata, 
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata

Whosoever Sings This Aarti To Lakshmi Will Get Rid Of Sins And Will Attain Happiness.

 #OmJaiLaxmiMata #LaxmiMataAarti #AlkaYagnik #Dhanteras #JaiLaxmiMata #diwali2022  #DiwaliAarti #MataAarti #MahaLakshmi #महालक्ष्मी #aarti #bhajan #Lakshmi #JaiMaaLakshmi

snippet.title: गौराई गं आली | Gaurai Ga Ali |  Gauri-Ganpati Festival Special |  Savaniee Ravindrra | Marathi Song
snippet.description:
गौराई गं आली | Gaurai Ga Ali |  Gauri-Ganpati Festival Special |  Savaniee Ravindrra | Savaniee Originals | Marathi Song | Mangalagaur 

About Video 
------------------------------------
नमस्कार! गणपती बाप्पांच्या आगमनानंतर गौराईचे स्वागत हा आपल्या संस्कृतीतील एक अतिशय भावनिक आणि शुभ प्रसंग असतो. त्या सुंदर क्षणांना समर्पित "गौराई गं आली" हे नवे गाणं, Savaniee Original’s Series कडून आपल्या सेवेत सादर करत आहोत.

Gaurai Ga Ali – A melodious and divine Marathi song dedicated to the arrival of Gaurai during Ganpati festival. This heartfelt track celebrates the emotional joy, devotion, and warmth of this sacred tradition in every Marathi home.

🙏 स्वागत करूया गौराईचे – प्रेमाने, भक्तीने आणि आनंदाने!

About Savaniee Ravindrra
--------------------------------------------
Savaniee Ravindrra is an acclaimed Indian playback singer and the recipient of the 67th National Film Award for Best Female Playback Singer for the film Bardo.

She has lent her voice to songs in multiple Indian languages including Marathi, Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali, Gujarati, Konkani, and Malayalam.

With over 500 performances across the globe, Savaniee has shared the stage with legends like:
🎤 Pt. Hridaynath Mangeshkar
🎤 Hariharan
🎤 Shaan
🎤 Suresh Wadkar
🎤 Ravindra Jain
🎤 Ajay-Atul and many more.
------------------------------------

📘 Facebook: Savaniee Official
